title: No Kayle Skin / Kayle / Icon
body: Uh... I haven't received my Kayle Riot Skin or the Icon for the 10 year anniversary yet and I've been playing since Season 4 and I have also been playing a lot for the past few months. Is it taking time for the gifts to be sent out to all the players or something?

replies.body: been playing for 5 year and accounts created this year already have it ... But ok rito

It is indeed taking time to send gifts with all of the eligible players!  You can stay updated through our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Gifts will be sent out individually, so hang tight!
Ok, nvm. I found the Kayle Skin. There just wasn't an alert saying that I received one. But I still don't have the Icon yet.
